  </div>
  <div class="nav-item" id="nav-figure" onclick="showFigureView(this)">
    <span class="nav-icon fig-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>鍥惧儚缁樺埗
  </div>

  <div class="nav-label">鏈€杩戝璇?/div>
  <div class="recent-list" id="recent-list">
    <div class="recent-empty">鏆傛棤鍘嗗彶瀵硅瘽</div>
  </div>

  <div class="nav-bottom">
    <div class="usage-wrap">
      <div class="usage-row">
        <span>浠婃棩瀵硅瘽</span><span id="usage-txt">0 娆?/span>
      </div>
      <div class="usage-track"><div class="usage-fill" id="usage-fill" style="width:0%"></div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="nav-item" id="nav-settings" onclick="showSettingsView(this)">
      <span class="nav-icon">鈿欙笍</span>璁剧疆
    </div>
