          <div class="write-paper">
            <div class="write-paper-top"><span class="write-dot"></span><span>Prompt Draft</span><span style="margin-left:auto">Markdown ready</span></div>
            <textarea id="writing-brief" class="write-textarea large" placeholder="鍐欐竻妤氫綘鎯崇敓鎴愮殑鍐呭銆佸凡鏈夎鐐广€佸繀椤昏鐩栫殑瑕佺偣銆佸笇鏈涢伩鍏嶇殑闂銆備緥锛氳鏍规嵁鎴戠殑鐭ヨ瘑搴擄紝鍐欎竴娈靛叧浜庡皬鐩爣妫€娴嬫寫鎴樹笌澶氬昂搴︾壒寰佽瀺鍚堟柟娉曠殑 related work锛岃姹備繚鐣欏紩鐢ㄧ嚎绱紝璇█姝ｅ紡锛岄伩鍏嶈櫄鏋勫疄楠岀粨鏋溿€?></textarea>
          </div>
          <textarea id="writing-material" class="write-textarea" placeholder="鍙€夛細绮樿创闇€瑕佹敼鍐?鎵╁啓鐨勫師鏂囷紝鎴栧垪鍑哄繀椤讳娇鐢ㄧ殑绱犳潗瑕佺偣銆?></textarea>
          <div class="write-upload">
            <div class="write-upload-icon">馃搸</div>
            <div style="min-width:0;flex:1">
              <div class="write-upload-title">涓婁紶鍐欎綔绱犳潗</div>
              <div class="write-upload-sub">鏀寔 PDF銆丳PTX銆乀XT銆丮arkdown銆備笂浼犲悗浼氳繘鍏ュ綋鍓嶄細璇濓紝Writing Agent 浼氫紭鍏堜娇鐢ㄨ繖浜涚礌鏉愩€?/div>
            </div>
            <input id="writing-file-input" type="file" multiple accept=".pdf,.pptx,.txt,.md,.text,.rst" style="display:none" onchange="uploadWritingFiles(this)">
            <button class="write-secondary" onclick="document.getElementById('writing-file-input').click()">閫夋嫨鏂囦欢</button>
          </div>
